    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly car with plenty of life left for the right buyer. It\u2019s not a showpiece, but it starts, runs, and offers a practical, affordable way to get around. Great option for a commuter, first car, or someone who doesn\u2019t mind a little cosmetic wear in exchange for real value. Priced to sell and worth a look if you want inexpensive transportation without the fuss.",
