      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Sharp-looking project car with solid enthusiast potential and a drivetrain that still shows life. The engine pulls through the rev range, the transmission engages, and the chassis has the kind of direct, mechanical feel that makes these worth saving. Not a showroom example and it will need cosmetic and general sorting, but it\u2019s a complete, usable platform with good bones for someone who wants an affordable driver-project, weekend build, or parts-friendly restoration candidate. Priced to move for the buyer who recognizes a worthwhile foundation.",
