    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of honest, road-worn character you can\u2019t fake\u2014a machine with stories in its bones and plenty of life left for the right driver. Whether you\u2019re looking for a budget-friendly runabout, a practical backup, or a rewarding project to make your own, it offers a rare chance to get behind the wheel without stretching your wallet. Full of grit, presence, and possibility, this is the sort of car that appeals to someone who sees potential instead of polish.",
      "price": 5950.0,
