      "description": "Affordable, straightforward transportation with solid value for a budget-minded buyer. This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and is best suited for someone seeking inexpensive mobility, a project, or a practical backup car. Priced to reflect its condition, it presents a cost-effective way to get into a vehicle without overpaying. A sensible opportunity for the right buyer.",
