    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of life left to give? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option for someone who wants dependable basic transport, a project, or a handy runabout. It has the kind of honest wear you\u2019d expect at this price, and that\u2019s exactly what makes it such a great value. If you want something cheap, straightforward, and ready for its next chapter, this could be a smart buy.",
      "price": 4950.0,
